{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhtbyjlmo1s0","created":1776215821431,"text":"navigation_transport.launch"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhte59aqt7k0","created":1776221989774,"text":"navigation_transport_node","layout_right_offset":{"x":-28.000000300913257,"y":-348.00000373992214},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtk38n6co00","created":1776238758280,"text":" self.create_service(SetPose2D, '~/pick', self.start_pick_srv_callback) \n #创建服务，供外部调用导航抓取点的接口\n此处暂未使用，可能在语音指令处调用","priority":null,"layout_right_offset":{"x":7.0000000752283995,"y":-253.00000271896636},"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtkkjjxwjk0","created":1776240114220,"text":"self.create_service(SetPose2D, '~/place', self.start_place_srv_callback)\n #创建服务端，供外部调用导航放置点的接口\n客户端在：automatic_pick.py","priority":1,"layout_right_offset":{"x":30.000000322407118,"y":-210.00000225684948},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtle15z6hc0","created":1776242425118,"text":"回调函数;start_place_srv_callback(self, request, response)\n主要功能：等待客户端发送一个目标点的欧拉角坐标发送过来，然后转换这个坐标为，最后再这个坐标上插上旗子","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtpi2ixojs0","created":1776254025976,"text":"发布话题：self.mark_pub.publish(markerArray)\n话题类型：path_point\n功能： 把旗子发给 RViz 显示出来","layout_right_offset":{"x":13.000000139709755,"y":-80.00000085975216}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtpi6xb0qo0","created":1776254035551,"text":"发布话题：self.nav_pub.publish(pose)  \n话题类型：self.nav_goal\n 功能：发布这个目标坐标","layout_right_offset":{"x":32.00000034390064,"y":122.0000013111221}},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhtm7iub7dc0","created":1776244736155,"text":"self.create_subscription(PoseStamped, self.nav_goal, self.goal_callback, 1, callback_group=timer_cb_group)\n话题类型  ：self.nav_goal\n功能：#订阅导航目标点话题，供外部调用\n回调函数：goal_callback","layout_right_offset":{"x":66.00000070929548,"y":1.1368683772161603e-13},"layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhte5ie2lrk0","created":1776222009566,"text":"automatic_pick_launch","layout_right_offset":{"x":15.000000161203616,"y":-96.00000103170271},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhte6ajp7yo0","created":1776222070856,"text":"automatic_pick","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtli6mgb5s0","created":1776242750455,"text":"self.transport_client = self.create_client(SetPose2D, '/navigation_transport/place')\n #创建服务客户端，用于在拾取完成后将放置位置发送给导航模块，以便导航模块能够引导机器人前往正确的放置位置","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhte64idxjc0","created":1776222057716,"text":"navigation_launch","layout_right_offset":{"x":40.00000042987608,"y":-28.00000030091337},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhte6gbh8740","created":1776222083420,"text":"bringup.launch","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhtpuu2ape80","created":1776255026288,"text":"rviz_node","layout_right_offset":{"x":52.00000055883902,"y":-421.0000045244459}},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtpv8oku600","created":1776255058111,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}